      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem to believe it! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is just pristine\u2014it even still has that new-car smell! I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping this beauty in top-notch shape, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you! \u2728 Drop me a message and come take a look!",
